ETI_Unknown_chairman_statement_35_0,ETI,ETI,Banking,Unknown,manual_pdf,chairman_statement,"Group did not lose focus. They continued to serve our customers, execute on strategy and deliver results, meeting and in many cases exceeding the ambitious targets set by the Board through management. That combination of professional integrity and commercial focus, maintained under pressure, speaks to the character of this institution and its people.

