NB_2023_outlook_9_0,NB,Nigerian Breweries Plc,Consumer Goods,2023,annual_report,outlook,"Nigerian Breweries Plc is proud to be one of a select group of companies that has not only withstood the ups and downs of an ever changing and challenging business environment but has remained one of Nigeria's topmost companies over the last eight decades. We look forward with excitement to celebrating, in the course of 2026, our eighty years of resilience and success.

