UNILEVER_Unknown_operating_review_4_0,UNILEVER,UNILEVER,Consumer Goods,Unknown,manual_pdf,operating_review,"In 2025, we became a more focused and agile Unilever, delivering on our commitment to volume-driven growth and strong gross margin. We generated turnover of €50.5 billion, operating profit of €9.0 billion, net profit of €6.2 billion and free cash flow of €5.9 billion.

Turnover was down (3.8)% versus the prior year. Underlying sales growth contributed 3.5%, offset by a significant currency impact of (5.9)% and (1.2)% from disposals, net of acquisitions. The currency impact was primarily driven by Latin American currencies, the Indian rupee, the US dollar and the Turkish lira, all depreciating against the euro.",97,good,,,,,,,,pending
